reviews.review:
Where to start:
- There has been a bug that prevented all survs to gain Survival points, in such a way that was impossibile to gain or even not to lose pips, causing a painful downhill to purple ranks;
-There has been another bug the prevented survs from seeing where the killer really was, so most of the time you were hit by wi-fi hits;
-There is (yet another) bug that make all pleyrs disconnect from steam servers. Okay, that's not on you but losing 2 pips from a problem THAT IS NOT MINE doesn't sound legit;
-Lately there is this new bug that even though you gain enough emblems to not lose your rank you still do! It's incredible how these bugs never work the other way;
I would like to put a pic of this bug here but it seems that I can't, so if you're interested in it you can check my profile;
There as been a bug as killer that you couldn't pick up people exiting from closets, so survs started exploiting it making it possible to survive and stall longer.
Instead of realeasing new killers with some "EmOtIoNaL bAcKgRoUnD" and "OmG iT's KpOp" try resolving some bugs, so people can still enjoy playing this game

I almost forgot: thanks to the most advanced videogame technology available in 2021 at the end of the match you automatically get bald
